data.description: The living is easy in this impressive and contemporary residence with panoramic views of the Black Hills. The floor plan encompasses five spacious bedrooms and three luxurious bathrooms with custom tile work. The sleek and stylish kitchen flows through to the dining room and living room. It boasts high end appliances, bamboo floors and stone island. The master bedroom is complete with a walk-in closet, soaking tub and deck access. Last, but not least, enjoy the downstairs living area, which features a wet bar and may accommodate pool table, theater and more! This home is ideally located minutes to downtown Sturgis making it the perfect Rally retreat, as well as, a great family home. Call Jake Johnson with The Real Estate Group to schedule a private showing today. 605-280-4481
data.whatILove:
Panoramic View! This large ranch style home features an open floor plan with vaulted ceilings in the living room and kitchen. Main-level includes 3 
bedrooms and 2 baths. Lower-level also features an open floor plan with additional rooms and a full bathroom. This beautiful home has been upgraded with
Quartz countertops throughout. Custom kitchen features bamboo flooring and comes with upper end stainless steel appliances, drop sink, stone tile bar,
island and pantry. All bathrooms feature custom tile work. Master bathroom features walk-in shower with soaker tub, double drop in sink and edgeless glass
shower door along with huge master closet. Built-in blinds in back doors.Stucco and faux rock exterior for low maintenance. Two redwood decks span the
back of the home and is accessible from master bedroom and kitchen. Lower deck is accessible from downstairs living area which features a wet bar, new
carpet throughout and open concept. Upstairs living area features electric fireplace.
